JESComponent.4.Scale:               Pt
JESComponent.4.Group:               2

JESComponent.5.Name:                Rtrk_Modelling_mass
JESComponent.5.Param:               PtMassAbsEta
JESComponent.5.Scale:               Mass
JESComponent.5.Group:               2


# Rtrk tracking components (pT + mass)
